  18,8,Menen ko Men wa…óoo…ìe ko woni kon e hoore mayri boowol yoorungal
  18,9,"Kaa a sikku no yim…ìe fammeere=wimmba nden e binndi …óin, …óun wonu immorde e Aayeeje Amen hawnii…óe"
  18,10,"Tuma nde sukaa…ìe …ìen sorunoo ka fammeere, …ìe wi'i: \"Joomi amen okku men immorde ka Maa…óa Hinnayee=yurmeende newinaNaa men kadi e fiyaake amen peewal"
  18,11,Men piyi e dow noppi ma…ì…ìe …óin ka nder fammeere limoore duu…ìi
  18,12,"Refti Men immintini …ìe fii yo Men fen√±inir gonndal ko honnde e mojobe=pelle …óen …ói…ói …ìuri moftude [limoore] ko …ìe √±ii…ìi kon dummunne"
  18,13,"Menen Me…óen fillanaade ma kumpital fii ma…ì…ìe e Goonga, …ìen …óon, ko sukaa…ìe gom…óin…ìe Joomi ma…ì…ìe Men …ìeydani …ìe Peewal"
  18,14,"Men ha…ì…ìi e dow …ìer…óe ma…ì…ìe tuma nde …ìe darinoo, …ìe wi'i: \"Joomi amen ko Jey…óo On kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, men noddataa ko woori Mo rewetee…óo, gom…óii haray men wi'ii ontuma [konngol] fantungol"
  18,15,"∆Åee yim…ìe amen, …ìe jogitike ko woori Mo rewetee…ói, ko haaanunoo ko yo …ìe addu e dow ma…ì…ìe dalil …ìanngu…óo. Ko hommbo …ìuri too√±ude ko foti e on fefindii…óo fenaande o fawi e Alla"
  18,16,"Tuma nde wo…ó…óitino…óon …ìe e ko …ìe rewata kon ko woori Alla, …ìe soroyi ka fammeere Joomi mon fontani on e Yurmeende Makko nden O newinani on e fiyaake mon neweende"
  18,17,"Hi…óa yi'a naangi ngen si nge ∆¥ellitike hinge naayora ka fammeere ma…ì…ìe senngo √±aamo, si hinge mutude nge mutiranay …ìe ka senngo nano, kam…ìe hi…ìe e yaajeende e …óun, …óun ko jeyaa…óun e Aayeeje Alla, on mo Alla fewni ko on woni feewu…óo, kala moO majjini a he…ìantaa mo hettu…óo fewnoowo. @Corrected"
  18,18,"Hi…óa sikka …ìe ko …ìe finu…ìe, hara kam…ìe ko …ìe …óaanii…ìe, Me…óen waylitira …ìe senngo √±aamo e senngo nano, rawaandu ma…ì…ìe ndun no fonti kay…óe mun …óen ka dammbugal, si a ∆¥ellitike e ma…ì…ìe a huccitayno e ma…ì…ìe dogaa a heewayno kulol immorde e ma…ì…ìe"
  18,19,"Ko nii Men immintiniri …ìe fii yo …ìe lanndondir hakkunde ma…ì…ìe, wi'oowo wi'i immorde e ma…ì…ìe: \"No foti hewde ko √±ii…ìu…óon?\" ∆Åe wi'i: \"Men √±ii…ìii √±allal maa go…ó…óun e √±allal.\" ∆Åe wi'i: \"Ko Joomi mon woni Anndu…óo emmbere ko √±ii…ìu…óon, nulee go…ó…óo e mon wonndude e …óii kaaki=ceede mon …óoo ka saare, yo o ndaaru ko hommbo e ma…ì…ìe …ìuri laa…ìude √±aamitee, yo o addan on √±aametee immorde e on …óon, yo o molto wata gooto so'u fii mon"
  18,20,"Pellet, kam…ìe si …ìe ∆¥ellitike e mon …ìe rajmay on, maa…óun …ìe rutta on e laawol ma…ì…ìe ngol, ontuma hara on maletaake poomaa"
  18,21,"Ko nii Men yaltiniri fii ma…ì…ìe, fii yo …ìe anndu pellet, Fodoore Alla nden ko nde Goonga, Pellet, Darngal ngal sikke alaa e maggal. Tuma nde …ìe poo…óondiraynoo hakkunde ma…ì…ìe fiyaake ma…ì…ìe …óen, …ìe wi'i: \"Mahee e hoore ma…ì…ìe maadi, ko Joomi ma…ì…ìe woni Anndu…óo fii Ma…ì…ìe.\" ∆Åen foolu…ìe e fiyaake mu'un wi'i: \"Men jogitoto e dow ma…ì…ìe Juulirde"
  18,22,"Aray …ìe wi'a: \"Ko …ìe tato naya…ìo ma…ì…ìe ko rawaandu ma…ì…ìe ndun.\" ∆Åe wi'a kadi: \"Ko …ìe njowo njeega…ìo ma…ì…ìe ko rawaandu ma…ì…ìe ndun ko fampaangol ka ni…ìe.\" ∆Åe wi'a kadi: \"Ko …ìe njee…ói…óo njeetata…ìo ma…ì…ìe ko rawaandu ma…ì…ìe ndun.\" Maaku: \"Ko Joomi an woni Anndu…óo limoore ma…ì…ìe, anndaa …ìe si wanaa see…óaa…ìe.\" Wata a wennju fii ma…ì…ìe si wanaa yewtere fee√±unde, wata a lanndo fii ma…ì…ìe hay e gooto e ma…ì…ìe"
  18,23,"Wata a wi'an huunde: \"Min mi wa…óay …óun janngo"
  18,24,"Si wanaa si Alla Muuyii, janto Joomi maa…óa si a yejjitii, maaku: \"No tijjaa nde Joomi an Fewnan mi ko …ìuri …ìadaade immorde e …óun Peewal"
  18,25,"∆Åe √±ii…ìi ka fammeere ma…ì…ìe duu…ìi teeme…ó…óe tati, …ìe …ìeydi jeenay"
  18,26,"Maaku: \"Ko Alla woni Anndu…óo emmbere ko …ìe √±ii…ìi, ko Kanko heeranii ko wirnii kon ka kammuuli e ka leydi kaawes ko yi'iri wa Makko e ko naniri, alanaa …ìe gaanin Makko gi…óo, O kafidaa ka √ëaawoore Makko hay e gooto"
  18,27,"Janngu ko wahayinaa e maa…óa kon immorde e Deftere Joomi maa nden, alaa wattitoowo Daaluyeeji=konngudi Makko …óin, a he…ìataa gaanin Makko fattorde"
  18,28,"Tabintin wonkii maa…óa kin wonndude e …ìen noddoo…ìe Joomi ma…ì…ìe ka bimmbi e ka kiikii…óe hi…ìe faandii Jaati Makko Kin, wata gite maa …óe yawtu gaayi ma…ì…ìe hara hi…óa faandii cu…óaari ngurdan aduna, wota a …óofto on mo Men welsindini …ìernde mun gaayi jantagol Men o jokki belee…óe makko fiyaake makko on woni halkaare"
  18,29,"Maaku Goonga kan immorde ka Joomi mon, mono faalaa yo o gom…óin mono faalaa yo o yeddu, Menen Men heblanii too√±oo…ìe …ìen Yiite no hunnditi …ìe …óen…óe magge …óen si …ìe …óa…ì…ìii faabo, …ìe faaboree ndiyan wa'u…óan wa sila taynaa…óo …óan ju…óa geece …óen, bonii njaram bonii werde"
  18,30,"Pellet, …ìen gom…óin…ìe …ìe golli mo∆¥∆¥i …óin, Menen Men yeebataa njoddi kala mo∆¥∆¥in…óo golle"
  18,31,"∆Åen …óon no woodani …ìe Aljannaaji √±ii…ìal can…ói no ila ley ma…ì…ìe, hi…ìe cu…óiree ton immorde e jawe kan≈ãe …ìe …ìornoo conci haaki…óu…ói …óewlu…ói e jalbu…ói ko …ìe so…ì…ìindii…ìe=tuugiibe ton e hoore julle, mo∆¥∆¥ii mbarjaari mo∆¥∆¥ii kadi fowtorde"
  18,32,"fiyan …ìe misal,wor…ìe …ói…óo Men wa…óani go…ó…óo e ma…ì…ìe gese …ói…ói inab Menhunndintini =hurliride …óe tamarooje Men wa…ói hakkunde majje remuru"
  18,33,"∆äen gese …ói…ói kala addi √±aametee majje, …óe too√±aali hay e huunde e …óun, Men seeki hakkunde majje [gese …óen …ói…ói] caangol"
  18,34,"Wonani mo dim…óe, o wi'ani wonndii…óo makko on tawi himo yewtude mo: \"Min mi…óo …ìurumaa jawdi e teddude gorol"
