  18,36,"Mi sikkaa kdai Darngal ngal daroto, mi woondii si mi artira le ka Joomi an, maa mi tawu sanne, waylitorde …ìurnde mba mo∆¥∆¥ude"
  18,37,"Wonndii…óo makko on wi'ani mo, tawi himo yewtude mo: \"Enee, a yeddii On Tagu…óo ma immorde mbullaari=leydi refti e to…ì…ìere [maniiyu] refti O fonndumaa gorko"
