  18,40,No jortaa nde Joomi an okkoyta lan mo∆¥∆¥ere …ìurnde ngesa maa mban O nula e mabba lepte immorde ka kammu mba wonta boowal …ìowrungal
  18,41,"Maa…óun ndiyan mabba …óan wonta …ìee…ìu…óan, hara a hattantaake …óa…ì…ìugol …óan"
